$ Power Query Editor

The → Microsoft/Power-Query Editor allows to
  • preview → development/Data
  • apply over 300 data transformations

{ Viewing Formula-M

  In the Power Query Editor, the currenlty worked on → Microsoft/Power-Query/M-formula/language[M formula] can be seen using the Menu
  *View* -> *Advanced Editor*.

}

